			<div class="card mb-3" style="width: 100%;">
				<div class="card-header font-weight-bold" style="font-size: 25px;">Do you have any question?</div>
				<div class="card-body row align-items-top flex-md-row flex-column">
					<div class="col-md-9 col-lg-10 pb-4 pb-sm-0">
